            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2469Step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium heat</p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle of olive oil if your pan is looking a little dry!</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion </strong>and <strong>grated carrot </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 5 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
