    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>wholewheat spaghetti </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of salt and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>wholewheat spaghetti</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked wholewheat spaghetti </strong>and return it to the pot</p>",
